rows.label: qev041201_MSG0001
rows.name: Hrrmrmr... This bad. Very, very bad.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041201_MSG0002
rows.name: Muh? Friend has business with caravan?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041201_MSG0003
rows.name:
Well, caravan has no business with friend,
so move along. Go on, now! Git! Shoo![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041201_JNK0010
rows.name: Obey

rows.label: qev041201_SEL0011
rows.name: Do as you are told and leave.

rows.label: qev041201_JNK0020
rows.name: Refuse

rows.label: qev041201_SEL0021
rows.name: Say that you don't take orders from him.

rows.label: qev041201_MSG0004
rows.name: Hmm? Hmmmmm?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041201_MSG0005
rows.name: Friend is actually leaving? That not very fun...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041201_MSG0006
rows.name:
Well, today Mumun is in good mood, so Mumun will
do friend the favor of speaking for while.
Not long, though. Just little bit.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041201_MSG0007
rows.name:
Mumun might even allow friend to help out with
problem as extra-special treat![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041201_MSG0008
rows.name: No need to thank Mumun. Friend is welcome.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041201_MSG0009
rows.name: Hmm? Hmmmmm?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041201_MSG0010
rows.name: Friend dares to defy Mumun?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041201_MSG0011
rows.name:
Does friend know Mumun is the top student of
THE Mujiji?![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041201_MSG0012
rows.name: Ho! Oh ho! Oh ho ho hurf![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041201_MSG0013
rows.name:
Friend is so foolhardy, Mumun can only laugh!
Oh ho ho heh heh hurf hurf hurf![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041201_MSG0014
rows.name:
What an amusing human. Mumun like friend so much,
Mumun will allow friend the privilege of helping out
with little problem.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041201_MSG0015
rows.name: No need for thanks. Friend is welcome.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041201_MSG0016
rows.name: This caravan has many regular customers.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041201_MSG0017
rows.name:
Human friends are especially big spenders, but caravan
leader say that demographic too important for Mumun
to handle.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041201_MSG0018
rows.name:
Instead, Mumun stuck with stinky Prone in stronghold
to the southeast![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041201_MSG0019
rows.name:
Mumun currently peddling locally-harvested kiweggs
at wholesale prices. That something that not even most
desperate Nopon want to sell![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041201_MSG0020
rows.name:
Mumun only saddled with lousy assignment because
no one else want it.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041201_MSG0021
rows.name:
Even worse, Mumun has to sell kiweggs to Prone.
Prone huge! Prone scary! During last sales call,
one threaten to eat Mumun instead of kiweggs![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041201_MSG0022
rows.name:
Other Prone all laugh, so Mumun assume it was what
pass for Prone joke. But still not very funny.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041201_MSG0023
rows.name: And who can say that joke not become real next time?![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041201_MSG0024
rows.name:
Still, stinky Prone are paying customer. And if Mumun
ask to change assignment, Mujiji will say Mumun is
failure as merchant.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041201_MSG0025
rows.name:
So Mumun want to hire friend to guard body,
just to be sure Mumun not wind up as snack.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041201_MSG0026
rows.name:
Oh, but they are customers, so no threatening anyone
unless they don't behave![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041201_MSG0027
rows.name:
Friend just needs to pretend to be business partner
and stick close to Mumun. Veeery close.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev041201_MSG0028
rows.name: Mumun counting on friend![ST:wait ]
